{"tid":774639,"cid":7,"subCid":0,"title":"陸駿光師奶仔多NG","createTime":"2018-08-10T13:08:01.000Z","updateTime":"2018-08-10T13:08:01.000Z","uid":25558,"like":0,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":1,"replies":[{"pid":"3496bde7320efe686b8e4ae41baa6496b496d42a","tid":774639,"uid":25558,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-08-10T13:08:01.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"https://hk.entertainment.appledaily.com/entertainment/daily/article/20180810/20472731\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.entertainment.appledaily.com%2Fentertainment%2Fdaily%2Farticle%2F20180810%2F20472731&d=idlRQUqkF3qAdBQ7IAyxfaNGKT0mDZcTD8WJHRevFdc%3D&h=ca95226a\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.entertainment.appledaily.com%2Fentertainment%2Fdaily%2Farticle%2F20180810%2F20472731&h=f715f690\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://hk.entertainment.appledaily.com/entertainment/daily/article/20180810/20472731</a><br />\n<br />\n陸駿光師奶仔多NG<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://static.appledaily.hk/images/apple-photos/apple/20180810/large/10ec4p11.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fstatic.appledaily.hk%2Fimages%2Fapple-photos%2Fapple%2F20180810%2Flarge%2F10ec4p11.jpg&h=22c49ada&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n■陸駿光在NG片段中，不時爆笑又嘟嘴。<br />\n<br />\n<br />\nViuTV劇集《Plan B》雖然劇情沉重，但陸駿光在戲外十分搞笑，與他飾演的冷血殺手「閻羅」有很大反差，連對手陳啟泰（Ken）都笑他平時是「師奶仔」，陸駿光笑言刻意搞笑是為容易入戲。<br />\n<br />\n從NG片段中，見陸駿光拍攝時有幾次忍不住笑︰「場戲講Ken哥攞咗我女友隻手指，因為我哋喺現場睇隻手指已經好似條膶腸，Ken哥要吮隻手指，之後要用牙籤拮，但因為幾次都拮到跌落地，所以我咪忍唔住笑囉。」他又說：「感恩呢齣劇畀咗好好嘅經驗我，以前我見到好多演員埋機前好輕鬆，好似吳鎮宇咁。自己做咗十幾年戲，發覺原來要學放鬆，咁至唔會框死自己。」<br />\n<br />\n採訪︰祖李"}]}